{"title":"7. 用AI做KV设计","slug":"baq0td8g5swtgzec","summary":"原文链接： https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/3Y6f0vRLihLyckFbeN6DCg ​ AI技术的崛起和成熟给各行业带来了巨大的变革，设计行业更是面临着巨大的挑战和变化。 在当前阶段，AI是否能够取代设计师仍然存在非常大的讨论和疑问。但不管怎样，在AI","category":"PART7️⃣ 设计全流程AI提效指南","tags":["PART7️⃣ 设计全流程AI提效指南"],"featured":false,"order":114,"level":1,"updatedAt":"2025-08-04","wordCount":817,"sourceUrl":"https://www.yuque.com/abyssalsailor/yg90qa/baq0td8g5swtgzec","html":"<blockquote data-lake-id=\"u42f194be\" id=\"u42f194be\"><p data-lake-id=\"u9be07fb3\" id=\"u9be07fb3\"><span data-lake-id=\"ucb7c2e83\" id=\"ucb7c2e83\">原文链接：</span><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/3Y6f0vRLihLyckFbeN6DCg\" target=\"_blank\" data-lake-id=\"u5303c422\" id=\"u5303c422\"><span data-lake-id=\"ub3962356\" id=\"ub3962356\">https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/3Y6f0vRLihLyckFbeN6DCg</span></a></p></blockquote><p data-lake-id=\"u49f293ba\" id=\"u49f293ba\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span data-lake-id=\"uec1b5b3c\" id=\"uec1b5b3c\">​</span><br></p><p data-lake-id=\"ud1c22492\" id=\"ud1c22492\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span data-lake-id=\"u15726b8a\" id=\"u15726b8a\">AI技术的崛起和成熟给各行业带来了巨大的变革，设计行业更是面临着巨大的挑战和变化。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u5aae0886\" id=\"u5aae0886\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span data-lake-id=\"u5ba78fc3\" id=\"u5ba78fc3\">在当前阶段，AI是否能够取代设计师仍然存在非常大的讨论和疑问。但不管怎样，在AI时代，设计师都将面对的是如何利用AI，结合自身的专业能力更好地完成设计需求。那么，钉钉的设计师又是如何借助AI技术来应对一场发布会的设计呢？今天就跟大家分享下。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u14829b36\" id=\"u14829b36\" style=\"text-align: center\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2024%2Fwebp%2F1206632%2F1730785475843-f1f3d126-758e-485a-aecd-9bdbed105a7d.webp%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u01a5bec1-ce06-43e4-ac94-090917fb9be%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u18e1d324-a01b-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1080%2C%22originHeight%22%3A607%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%233c4e84%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22ubd47c009%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\"></card></p><p data-lake-id=\"uea72a6bb\" id=\"uea72a6bb\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span data-lake-id=\"ufa77d438\" id=\"ufa77d438\"><br /><br /></span></p><h1 data-lake-id=\"p9JTD\" id=\"p9JTD\"><span data-lake-id=\"u2a7b7e04\" id=\"u2a7b7e04\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 127, 255)\">#01.</span><span data-lake-id=\"u96b782f6\" id=\"u96b782f6\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(0, 127, 255)\">创意阶段</span></h1><h2 data-lake-id=\"xWIxU\" id=\"xWIxU\"><span data-lake-id=\"ue203fe65\" id=\"ue203fe65\">1-1. 需求背景</span></h2><p data-lake-id=\"u93a2979a\" id=\"u93a2979a\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span data-lake-id=\"ubef6ddce\" id=\"ubef6ddce\">本次设计需求是设计活动主KV，活动主题“超级钉钉”，需要体现出钉钉、超级、科技、AI时代、B端等关键词。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u6d807a83\" id=\"u6d807a83\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span data-lake-id=\"u818b5b31\" id=\"u818b5b31\">如果直接用需求brief让AI来生成主视觉，显然AI无法完全理解，所以与AI的协作过程就像是甲方与乙方合作一样，需要设计师来拆解和理解需求，然后通过自己对需求的理解，给AI明确的指示，需求越明确，完成的也越符合预期</span></p><h2 data-lake-id=\"shc9M\" id=\"shc9M\"><span data-lake-id=\"ufd31c135\" id=\"ufd31c135\">1-2. 创意发散<br /><br /></span></h2><p data-lake-id=\"u051176ea\" id=\"u051176ea\" style=\"text-align: center\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2024%2Fwebp%2F1206632%2F1730785475851-6efb59f5-c211-44a4-947d-8d4058bea548.webp%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22ub278f3d6-183d-4f3c-8bc0-77881938103%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u18e1d324-a01b-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1080%2C%22originHeight%22%3A1146%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%231d272f%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u072fe863%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\"></card></p><p data-lake-id=\"u838f5b9e\" id=\"u838f5b9e\"><br></p><h1 data-lake-id=\"TErjh\" id=\"TErjh\"><span data-lake-id=\"ue9ca2d1b\" id=\"ue9ca2d1b\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 127, 255)\">#02.</span><span data-lake-id=\"u29deb5fa\" id=\"u29deb5fa\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(0, 127, 255)\">草图阶段</span></h1><p data-lake-id=\"ud6ed4a92\" id=\"ud6ed4a92\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span data-lake-id=\"u5dbe388f\" id=\"u5dbe388f\">有了创意想法之后便进入动手尝试的阶段。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"uc2e3ba56\" id=\"uc2e3ba56\" style=\"text-align: justify\"><span data-lake-id=\"ubdccb618\" id=\"ubdccb618\">因为涉及到相对具体的：图形体现、创意表达、风格、排版等方面的需求，所以我选择使用的AI工具是可控度较高的</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u3feb1867\" id=\"u3feb1867\" style=\"background-color: rgb(206, 231, 255)\">Stable Diffusion</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u7a2743a5\" id=\"u7a2743a5\">。</span></p><h2 data-lake-id=\"CkCah\" id=\"CkCah\"><span data-lake-id=\"u227a3f4e\" id=\"u227a3f4e\">2-1. 使用AI进行主题性设计时的困难</span></h2><p data-lake-id=\"uf5a13827\" id=\"uf5a13827\" style=\"text-align: center\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2024%2Fwebp%2F1206632%2F1730785475908-d24a0bbb-da13-47ea-bf08-bcf72321a9e6.webp%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u4087cea7-a620-4db1-8477-cbdef4741de%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u18e1d324-a01b-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1080%2C%22originHeight%22%3A670%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%232d3741%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u2ecb7d08%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\"></card></p><h2 data-lake-id=\"EcmJd\" id=\"EcmJd\"><span data-lake-id=\"u7d452402\" id=\"u7d452402\">2-2. 精准控制画面的方法</span></h2><p data-lake-id=\"u40baf260\" id=\"u40baf260\" style=\"text-align: center\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2024%2Fwebp%2F1206632%2F1730785475874-ee14ba71-6bdf-4eed-bc09-0a940cd398e0.webp%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u439b18a1-1605-42dc-9865-0ac6dcdcbba%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u18e1d324-a01b-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1080%2C%22originHeight%22%3A1076%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%231d242b%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u80af37fa%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\"></card></p><h2 data-lake-id=\"YIU9J\" id=\"YIU9J\"><span data-lake-id=\"ueeb73304\" id=\"ueeb73304\">2-3.将想法具体化</span></h2><p data-lake-id=\"ufe15b7ae\" id=\"ufe15b7ae\" style=\"text-align: center\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2024%2Fwebp%2F1206632%2F1730785475851-a62d9947-097e-4c7f-94f9-6cce8c1f7b55.webp%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u6bb0694d-bed0-426b-a1f1-07c69db5d4b%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u18e1d324-a01b-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1080%2C%22originHeight%22%3A1506%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23202528%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u8e1b7690%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\"></card></p><p data-lake-id=\"u43c73402\" id=\"u43c73402\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span data-lake-id=\"ue96bb454\" id=\"ue96bb454\"><br /><br /></span></p><h1 data-lake-id=\"lAS4T\" id=\"lAS4T\"><span data-lake-id=\"u3e88ef9f\" id=\"u3e88ef9f\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 127, 255)\">#03.</span><span data-lake-id=\"uce090f2c\" id=\"uce090f2c\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(0, 127, 255)\">生成阶段</span></h1><h2 data-lake-id=\"vRkG4\" id=\"vRkG4\"><span data-lake-id=\"u0e53b53a\" id=\"u0e53b53a\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(0, 127, 255)\">​</span><span data-lake-id=\"u9820d12f\" id=\"u9820d12f\">3-1. 大小模型的作用和选择</span></h2><p data-lake-id=\"uda432eb9\" id=\"uda432eb9\" style=\"text-align: left\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2024%2Fwebp%2F1206632%2F1730785476788-21d279fc-d817-48b9-9705-c136fe41c3f1.webp%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u8cb3ef26-3f8d-4b5e-8190-52ee7b9162c%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u18e1d324-a01b-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1080%2C%22originHeight%22%3A1173%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%2324282c%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u571c6b25%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\"></card><span data-lake-id=\"u5b75605f\" id=\"u5b75605f\"><br /><br /></span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u9833949a\" id=\"u9833949a\" style=\"text-align: left\"><span data-lake-id=\"u58ce4f2c\" id=\"u58ce4f2c\" style=\"background-color: rgb(206, 231, 255)\">🔥</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"udbe7f194\" id=\"udbe7f194\" style=\"background-color: rgb(206, 231, 255)\">需要注意的是：</span></strong></p><p data-lake-id=\"u7cfd17cc\" id=\"u7cfd17cc\" style=\"text-align: left\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ud6222fa8\" id=\"ud6222fa8\">只有在前期对画面内容有了一定的想象和预期的前提下，后续的模型挑选和测试，才能更高效的进行</span></strong><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u5dd81438\" id=\"u5dd81438\">，</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u9cff4c82\" id=\"u9cff4c82\">否则会比较容易陷入到不停「尝试—换方向—尝试」的循环中。</span><span data-lake-id=\"u95bca13e\" id=\"u95bca13e\">这也与我个人对设计的理解类似：</span><span data-lake-id=\"u1e1adac3\" id=\"u1e1adac3\">设计结果的好坏，其核心不在于挑选工具或是动手操作的环节，而在于能否从专业的角度进行思考和创意。</span></p><h2 data-lake-id=\"vIH4P\" id=\"vIH4P\"><span data-lake-id=\"u4fcbc6fc\" id=\"u4fcbc6fc\">3-2. 权重</span></h2><p data-lake-id=\"ubdc84baf\" id=\"ubdc84baf\" style=\"text-align: center\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2024%2Fwebp%2F1206632%2F1730785476901-2541a5f4-21b1-4c4f-9cae-a20088755245.webp%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u50bb6b26-64a8-4ba7-8b82-1fa94420723%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u18e1d324-a01b-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1080%2C%22originHeight%22%3A1055%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%231d262f%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u32f06a45%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\"></card><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ueef9e875\" id=\"ueef9e875\"><br /><br /></span></strong></p><h2 data-lake-id=\"vbeD3\" id=\"vbeD3\"><span data-lake-id=\"u9e4d4126\" id=\"u9e4d4126\">3-3. 扩图</span></h2><p data-lake-id=\"u1a18a1ad\" id=\"u1a18a1ad\" style=\"text-align: center\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2024%2Fwebp%2F1206632%2F1730785476867-0446152b-1b95-42cc-b434-81c303077b99.webp%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u00a7b929-bf1c-4198-9078-02af1e53e06%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u18e1d324-a01b-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1080%2C%22originHeight%22%3A2594%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%231d2c3e%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22uddd0b4e1%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\"></card></p><h1 data-lake-id=\"pdQjg\" id=\"pdQjg\"><span data-lake-id=\"u30ae2097\" id=\"u30ae2097\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 127, 255)\">#04.</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u95318de1\" id=\"u95318de1\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(0, 127, 255)\">全过程总结</span></strong></h1><p data-lake-id=\"u09283e23\" id=\"u09283e23\" style=\"text-align: center\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2024%2Fwebp%2F1206632%2F1730785476857-fdbbf9f7-8cb7-4bf3-bf7e-1babb306f562.webp%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u233933f8-9e29-4e7b-ba72-d2165e39633%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u18e1d324-a01b-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22url%22%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1080%2C%22originHeight%22%3A3330%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23242c36%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u86552f72%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\"></card></p><p data-lake-id=\"u3cd02929\" id=\"u3cd02929\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u4e1b78ff\" id=\"u4e1b78ff\" class=\"lake-fontsize-24\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">​</span></strong><br></p><p data-lake-id=\"ub614a395\" id=\"ub614a395\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u5e68facb\" id=\"u5e68facb\" class=\"lake-fontsize-24\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">结语</span></strong></p><p data-lake-id=\"u135fcced\" id=\"u135fcced\" style=\"text-align: left\"><span data-lake-id=\"u2f4af84f\" id=\"u2f4af84f\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">从AI刚开始火起来以玩玩的心态进行尝试，到使用AI做真实的设计，其实设计的流程没有太大的变化，都是「拆解需求—创意发散—创意实现—修改细化—落地」的过程。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u97c066d2\" id=\"u97c066d2\" style=\"text-align: left\"><span data-lake-id=\"u493ee8e3\" id=\"u493ee8e3\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">AI在现阶段更多的是工具的定位，还不足以理解和满足各种各样设计需求，想要得到预期的设计结果，就要提供足够充足和明确的内容输入。设计师的工作内容的核心是在需求中发现和解决问题，画图只是整个工作流程中的一个环节而已。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u56e4f84e\" id=\"u56e4f84e\" style=\"text-align: left\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u28bbc68c\" id=\"u28bbc68c\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9)\">AI也许降低的是人们操作工具的门槛，但一定不是设计的门槛。</span></strong></p><p data-lake-id=\"u33375e3a\" id=\"u33375e3a\" style=\"text-align: left\"><span data-lake-id=\"u9c867d6f\" id=\"u9c867d6f\"><br /><br /></span></p>"}
